26#include "config.h"
27#include "CachedSVGDocumentReference.h"
28
29#include "CachedResourceHandle.h"
30#include "CachedResourceLoader.h"
31#include "CachedResourceRequest.h"
32#include "CachedResourceRequestInitiators.h"
33#include "CachedSVGDocument.h"
34
35namespace WebCore {
36
37CachedSVGDocumentReference::CachedSVGDocumentReference(const String& url)
38 : m_url(url)
39 , m_document(nullptr)
40 , m_loadRequested(false)
41{
42}
43
44CachedSVGDocumentReference::~CachedSVGDocumentReference()
45{
46 if (m_document)
47 m_document->removeClient(*this);
48}
49
50void CachedSVGDocumentReference::load(CachedResourceLoader& loader, const ResourceLoaderOptions& options)
51{
52 if (m_loadRequested)
53 return;
54
55 auto fetchOptions = options;
56 fetchOptions.mode = FetchOptions::Mode::SameOrigin;
57 CachedResourceRequest request(ResourceRequest(loader.document()->completeURL(m_url)), fetchOptions);
58 request.setInitiator(cachedResourceRequestInitiators().css);
59 m_document = loader.requestSVGDocument(WTFMove(request)).value_or(nullptr);
60 if (m_document)
61 m_document->addClient(*this);
62
63 m_loadRequested = true;
64}
65
66}
